AddressInfo.Title: Bedford Centre (Bedfortview)
AddressInfo.AddressLine1: c/o Smith & Van Der Linde Road, Bedfordview
AddressInfo.AccessComments:
Entry on Krikby Road	
Enter the circle, exit the circle to the mall ticket booth. Ater entering, turn right and follow the road to last ramp down. Enter the lower basement parking. The charge point will be visible from your location.
Entry on Smith Road	
Turn left to the entrance next to the Shell gas station. Enter through the ticket booth and turn to your left. The charge point will be visible from your location.

GeneralComments: Known as one of Johannesburg's premier fashion destinations. The DC fast charger is located in the lower level covered parking area as you enter from Smith Road.
